HEADWORD: Deflectionize
<hw>De*flec"tion*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To free
from inflections.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Deflectionized</qex> languages are said to be analytic.</q>
<rj><qau>Earle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deflective</ent>⟦br⟧
